response.overview: Bonnie Raitt - "Soundstage" PBS TV - Recorded at WTTW Studios, Chicago, Il  Dec 17th, 1974.  Special Guests Junior Wells, Buddy Guy and A.C. Reed  SETLIST  A Man Of Many Words (Buddy Guy) Little By Little (Junior Wells) I Wouldn't Have To Sing The Blues (Junior Wells) Mystery Train (Junior Wells) Love Me Like A Man Any Day Woman Under The Falling Sky Write Me A Few Of Your Lines Woman Be Wise Angel From Montgomery You Got To Feel It Everybodys' Cryin' Mercy (with Junior Wells) Big Road Blues (Everybody!)  Nice early pro-shot concert with Bonnie and some great luminaries.
